They are also a risk factor for several others.
This is extremely harmful to human health.
"There are still 1.5 million smokers in Quebec today," said spokesman André Beaulieu.
10 years after a smoker quits smoking, the risk of dying from cancer is halved.
Weight
Body weight and obesity are another risk factor for the disease, according to SCC.
